FBIS3-15408 "drsov044_o_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-044 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 Uzbekistan Russian Television Relays To Stop 7 Mar LD0503193494 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1800 GMT 5 Mar 94 LD0503193494 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Reports from Tashkent say that the relay of Russian Television programs on the territory of the republic will officially be stopped as of 7 March. The Russian channel has been handed over to the Uzbek Television Third Program. It will also partly be devoted to relaying programs from Turkey. This means that the 2-million Russian diaspora in Uzbekistan will no longer be able to watch Russian Television.
